<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Memphis</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Σαραπίωνι τῶν διαδόχων καὶ ὑποδιοικητῆι παρὰ Πτολεμαίου <choice><corr>Μακεδόνος</corr><sic>μακεδων</sic></choice> τῶν ἐν κατοχῇ 

    <lb n="2"/>ὄντων ἐν τῶι μεγάλωι Σαραπιείωι ἔτος τοῦτο ἑνδέκατον καὶ τῶν διδυμῶν. ἀπέδωκά σοι <subst><add place="inline">τὴν</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">τη<gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/></del></subst> παρὰ τοῦ 

    <lb n="3"/><subst><add place="inline">βασιλέως</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">βασιλειας</del></subst> καὶ τῆς <choice><corr>βασιλίσσης</corr><sic>βασιλισης</sic></choice> κεχρηματισμένην τῶν διδυμῶν ἔντευξιν ὑπὲρ τῶν καθηκόντων 

    <lb n="4"/>αὐταῖς κατ᾽ ἐνιαυτὸν καὶ συνέταξας ἀποδοῦναι τὸ τοῦ <num value="18">ιη</num> καὶ τοῦ <num value="19">ιθ</num> ἔλαιον καὶ <choice><corr>κῖκι</corr><sic>κικιος</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="5"/><choice><corr>ἐξενι<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">αύ</supplied>του</corr><sic>εξενιτου</sic></choice> ἐλαίου <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">με μ<add place="supralinear">ε</add></del> <choice><corr>με</corr><sic><g type="monogram"/></sic></choice><expan><ex cert="high">τρητὴν</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num> καὶ κίκιος <expan>με<ex cert="high">τρητὴν</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num>. περὶ μὲν οὖν τούτων <choice><corr>δῶι</corr><sic>δοι</sic></choice> σοι 

    <lb n="6"/>ὁ Σάραπις <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">κ</del> καὶ ἡ Εἶσις <choice><corr>ἐπαφροδι<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">σί</supplied>α<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ν</supplied></corr><sic>επαφροδια</sic></choice> <choice><corr>χάριν</corr><sic>χαρειν</sic></choice> μορφὴν πρὸς τὸν <choice><corr>βασιλέα</corr><sic>βασιλεια</sic></choice> καὶ τὴν βασίλισσαν δι᾽ <choice><corr>ἣν</corr><sic>ης</sic></choice> ἔχεις 

    <lb n="7"/>πρὸς <choice><corr>τὸ</corr><sic>τω</sic></choice> θεῖον ὁσιότητα. προσδεόμενος δ᾽ ἔτι τυχεῖν καὶ ἐν τούτοις <choice><corr>συνεργείας</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">συνεργειαις</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">συνεργιειας</del></subst></sic></choice> ἀξιῶ σε, <choice><corr>ἐπεὶ</corr><sic>επι</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="8"/>προορῶμαι <choice><corr>μή<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">πο</supplied>τε</corr><sic>μηδε</sic></choice> <choice><corr>χωρισθέντος</corr><sic>χωρισθεντοσθεντος</sic></choice> σου εἰς τοὺς ἄνω τόπους οὐ λάβωσιν αἱ δίδυμαι 

    <lb n="9"/>τὰ τοῦ εἰκοστοῦ ἔτους ἔλαιον καὶ κῖκι, νομίσαντα <subst><add place="inline">ὅτι</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">νομισαννομιτι</del></subst> σὺ ἰδίαι χρηματίζεις αὐταῖς 

    <lb n="10"/><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><choice><corr>ἔλαιον</corr><sic>ελαιν</sic></choice> καὶ κῖκι νομ</del> γράψαι Μεννίδει τῶι <subst><add place="inline">ἐπιμελητῇ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">επιμελητει</del></subst> ἀποδοῦναί μοι καὶ τούτου 

    <lb n="11"/><sic>του</sic> τοῦ ἔτους τὸν καθήκοντα ἐλαίου μετρητὴν καὶ κίκιος μετρητὴν 

    <lb n="12"/>μηδὲν <subst><add place="inline">ἀντιπεσόντα</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ανταπεσοντα</del></subst>. σοὶ δὲ <sic>σοι</sic> γίνοιτο ἀνθ᾽ ὧν πρὸς τὸ θεῖον <subst><add place="inline">ὁσίως</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">οσιω<gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/></del></subst> διάκεισαι 

    <lb n="13"/>καὶ <choice><corr>τῶν</corr><sic>τον</sic></choice> ἱεροδούλων καὶ τῶν ἐν τῷ <subst><add place="inline">ἱερῶι</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">σερωι</del></subst> πάντων <subst><add place="inline">ἀντιλαμβάνηι</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ανταλαμβανηι</del></subst> 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐπαφροδισία χάρις μορφὴ <choice><corr>εὐημερία</corr><sic>ευημεριαι</sic></choice> <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/></del> καὶ <supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ἐν</supplied> τοῖς ἄλλοις <choice><corr>εὐτυχία</corr><sic>ε<gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/>τυχιαι</sic></choice> <choice><corr>εὐτύχει</corr><sic>ευτυυχει</sic></choice>. </ab></div><div n="meta.3425" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3425" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notAfter="-0161-01-23">vor 23. Jan. 161 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3425" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Auf derselben Seite: UPZ I 44. Rückseite: UPZ I 43. Duplikate: UPZ I 33, 35 und 36.</p></div><div n="meta.3425" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 4: <date type="mentioned" notBefore="-0164" notAfter="-0163">164 - 163 v.Chr.</date></p><p>Z. 4: <date type="mentioned" notBefore="-0163" notAfter="-0162">163 - 162 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3425" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">UPZ</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">34</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">3425</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0245</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">34</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0245;1;34" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3